text: Namgyal Lhamu (born 5 April 1974), is an archer who internationally represented Bhutan Lhamu competed for Bhutan at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona, she finished 61st in the individual event, and the Bhutanese women's team finished 17th.Sports Reference Profile ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic archers of Bhutan Category:Archers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Bhutanese female archers
